author: craigmcc
msg: Modify the two-argument constructor so that read-only properties (i.e.
those with only a "get" method but no "set" method) are recognized.
WARNING:  This code will still fail on a write-only property, but the
workaround is to call one of the four-argument versions of the constructor
with a null for the getter method.
